#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.33/guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Access your application endpoint by using `https://your-domain-name:8443/`; for example, `https://your-domain-name:8443/hello`, and accept a self-signed certificate in the browser."
msgstr "Acceda al punto final de su aplicación utilizando `https://your-domain-name:8443/` por ejemplo `https://your-domain-name:8443/hello` y acepte un certificado autofirmado en el navegador."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.33/guides/tls-registry-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Keep the application running and request your first Let's Encrypt certificate."
